{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Viking Fish is an idle fishing game that docks at the bottom of your screen, allowing you to manage your Vikings while attending to other tasks.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986650/extras/FullscreenPreviewGIF.gif?t=1728301439\" /></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Your Vikings cycle through an endless loop of casting, fishing, reeling in, and resting. Each time they reel in an item, it belongs to one of three categories: junk, fish, or treasure. Each category has two levels of rarity, rewarding the following coins:</i> </p><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Junk (Common):</strong> 30 coins  <br></li><li><strong>Junk (Uncommon):</strong> 100 coins  <br></li><li><strong>Fish (Rare):</strong> 500 coins  <br></li><li><strong>Fish (Epic):</strong> 2,500 coins  <br></li><li><strong>Treasure (Legendary):</strong> 10,000 coins  <br></li><li><strong>Treasure (Mythic):</strong> 25,000 coins</li></ul><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Coins are used to unlock new Vikings, allowing you to fish for more items faster. Vikings can also be upgraded to:</i> </p><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Decrease the chance of finding junk <br></li><li>Increase the chance of finding treasure <br></li><li>Reduce resting time <br></li><li>Increase fishing speed</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986650/extras/UpgradePanelGIF2.gif?t=1728301439\" /><br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The stats tab keeps track of your progress and lifetime achievements, including:</strong></p><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Total coins earned<br></li><li>Total items fished<br></li><li>Total junk, fish, and treasure items fished<br></li><li>Detailed records for each individual item, showing how many times it has been fished</li></ul><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hovering over any item will display a tooltip with additional information.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>With 100 unique items to fish for and a wide range of achievements to unlock, Viking Fish offers a rich and rewarding idle experience.</strong></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First Item","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2986650/940fb6767d97d35e8e963a6943a15f42de385ccb.jpg"},{"name":"Item Bronze I","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2986650/e0bb06eeaab8ace639cf87ae990b1a87610ee9d0.jpg"},{"name":"Item Bronze II","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2986650/e0bb06eeaab8ace639cf87ae990b1a87610ee9d0.jpg"},{"name":"Item Bronze III","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2986650/e0bb06eeaab8ace639cf87ae990b1a87610ee9d0.jpg"},{"name":"Item Silver I","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2986650/be6e613d1d007d24fc1d2efb7b417b51bedfd3a7.jpg"},{"name":"Item Silver II","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2986650/be6e613d1d007d24fc1d2efb7b417b51bedfd3a7.jpg"},{"name":"Item Silver III","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2986650/be6e613d1d007d24fc1d2efb7b417b51bedfd3a7.jpg"},{"name":"Item Gold I","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2986650/6dd80663cc7fdc9020bd35e3dbb35e49a5f26f30.jpg"},{"name":"Item Gold II","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2986650/6dd80663cc7fdc9020bd35e3dbb35e49a5f26f30.jpg"},{"name":"Item Gold III","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2986650/6dd80663cc7fdc9020bd35e3dbb35e49a5f26f30.jpg"}],"total":50},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986650/page_bg_gener